cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for recognizing mentions of human senses in text. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves learning methods, which suggests it could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques, which could place it under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with recognizing unnamed entities, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
